title: Spotfire/Qlikview Developer
desc:
Job highlights
Identified by Google from the original job post
Qualifications
•
Bachelor’s Degree
•
5+ experience with Data Analytics tools like Spotfire, Qlik, Tableau.
•
5+ experience with visualization and reporting technologies (e.g
•
Spotfire, QlikView, Tableau, etc.)
•
5+ years strong experience in visualization tools with any one programming language like python , java
•
Master Degree in Computer Science or related field
9 more items
Responsibilities
•
The person will be a key part of the Application Development team, working on the visualization tool like Spotfire and the latest Big Data technologies within the Hadoop ecosystem
•
Delivery focus will be leveraging existing components such as hdfs, Hive, HBase, Pig, Flume, Spark and others that are in an incubation stage to build applications that solve business problems and requirements and building extensions to the platform to enhance the capability of the platform
•
Some of the key responsibilities will be developing applications on the data and visualization platform to onboard asset classes on to this platform and building applications for the desks to mine into this data that will be on boarded from this asset classes
More job highlights

title: Spotfire/Qlikview Developer
desc:
Job highlights
Identified by Google from the original job post
Qualifications
•
Bachelor’s Degree
•
5+ experience with Data Analytics tools like Spotfire, Qlik, Tableau.
•
5+ experience with visualization and reporting technologies (e.g
•
Spotfire, QlikView, Tableau, etc.)
•
5+ years strong experience in visualization tools with any one programming language like python , java
•
Master Degree in Computer Science or related field
9 more items
Responsibilities
•
The person will be a key part of the Application Development team, working on the visualization tool like Spotfire and the latest Big Data technologies within the Hadoop ecosystem
•
Delivery focus will be leveraging existing components such as hdfs, Hive, HBase, Pig, Flume, Spark and others that are in an incubation stage to build applications that solve business problems and requirements and building extensions to the platform to enhance the capability of the platform
•
Some of the key responsibilities will be developing applications on the data and visualization platform to onboard asset classes on to this platform and building applications for the desks to mine into this data that will be on boarded from this asset classes
More job highlights
